ermining the app\'s essential features. I\'m thinking of this as a Visual Art Director & Prompt Generator Workspace with an Interactive Mockup Creator. I\'m evaluating the Gemini API to either generate the final image directly using `gemini-3.5-flash` or `gemini-2.5-flash-image`, or to mock a preview with Gemini rewrites of the base prompt. I\'m also now considering a full-stack approach with Express + Vite since we\'ll leverage the Gemini API.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 5
      nanos: 528680512
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
