          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "                  A Vellum & Vestige monograph is never simply a book; it represents a physical, dense vault of memory and design excellence. This is why we emphasize the 12\"x9\" ratio and the high-density paper block. Our prompts must always explicitly specify these physical bounds to instruct AI models to render a realistic, weighty physical presence that commands respect."
