          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_UNCHANGED
        }
        lines {
          text: "                    <strong>Open Spreads:</strong> Raw emotional warmth. The textured deckled edges part to reveal high-quality photography centering profound human stories, grandparents, home, or household companions. It bridges the gap between premium modernist industrial design and deep internal emotion."
