  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Reviewing Successful Build**\n\nNow that the build is complete, I\'m carefully reviewing all the user\'s feedback. I\'m focusing specifically on ensuring every concern is fully and elegantly resolved. My initial focus is on the positioning editors; I\'m working to fully understand what the user meant to describe.\n\n\n**Simplifying User Interface**\n\nI\'ve completely removed the \"Foil Logo Hallmark Position\" element, keeping the panel focused and simple. The volume information is now beautifully offset in the visualizer, positioned about one-third of the way from the top. For the monogram, I\'ve implemented a locked, elegant bottom-centered layout, representing the monogram on the front cover as golden, script calligraphic letters (\360\235\222\261\360\235\222\261) with the full name below.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have fully refined the application based on your directions to make it an incredibly polished, one-click photorealistic image creation engine for **Vellum & Vestige**.\n\nHere is a summary of the design updates and new features implemented:\n\n### \360\237\214\237 Photorealistic Image Generation (\"Go\" Engine)\n* **One-Click Generation**: Added a prominent, gold-accented **[Generate Photorealistic Art]** button directly below the live canvas mockup. Clicking this launches the rendering sequence.\n* **Ambient Loading Phase**: During rendering, the preview area transforms into a gorgeous creative director loading screen that rotates evocative status cards (e.g., *\"Weaving pure European flax linen...\"*, *\"Applying hot gold foil leaf onto bottom-centered hallmark...\"*, *\"Orienting morning daylight rays...\"*).\n* **Instant Gallery Preview**: Once compiled by our backend server (powered securely by the `gemini-2.5-flash-image` model), the generated masterpiece is displayed inside a beautiful gallery-grade white frame.\n* **Direct Downloads**: Added an elegant **[Download Masterpiece]** action to save your content immediately for TikTok, Instagram Reels, Stories, or feed posts. You can select **\"Modify Settings\"** at any time to return to the draft.\n\n### \360\237\223\220 Cover Positioning & Logo Refinements\n* **Volume Positioning**: Adjusted the 2D monograph mockup so that the volume label and title (e.g., *Volume I: The Provenance*) are now positioned approximately **1/3 of the way from the top** rather than dead-centered.\n* **Hallmark at the Bottom**: Placed the beautiful, calligraphic, gold-embossed `\360\235\222\261\360\235\222\261` monogram and *Vellum & Vestige* signature centered near the bottom edge of the cover.\n* **Simplified Interface**: Removed the unneeded layout positioning editors as requested, keeping your workspace minimalist, focused, and aligned with your brand guide."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 2
      nanos: 851421480
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
